0003C6E0                            ; This bank end still lacks proven 0xFF7A/0xFF7B terminators, but several later internal
0003C6E0                            ; starts are now called out explicitly because they begin with the same 0x0960 / 0x0F00 /
0003C6E0                            ; 0x0B60-style header-like prefixes already seen in earlier tail blocks. Keep the names
0003C6E0                            ; structural until a loader or decompressor proves whether these are true block headers,
0003C6E0                            ; format variants, or nested substreams.
