00099200                            ; The later bytes now tighten further too: a 30-record fixed 16-byte band at 0x099649,
00099200                            ; then a short 3-byte lead-in plus 20 fixed 5-byte records at 0x099829, before the local-
00099200                            ; offset word list, packed byte band, repeated 0x01F1 words, and final word trailer leading
00099200                            ; into the already split descriptor records at 0x099920.
