00099920                            ; ROM range: 0x099920-0x099A84
00099920                            ; Front structured band inside the 0x098000-0x09F776 non-fill island.
00099920                            ;
00099920                            ; The first 0x60 bytes at 0x099920-0x09997F tighten cleanly into sixteen fixed 6-byte
00099920                            ; records. The following 0xF5 bytes at 0x099980-0x099A74 tighten into forty-nine fixed
00099920                            ; 5-byte records, followed by a 16-byte tail at 0x099A75-0x099A84. The bytes strongly
00099920                            ; support stable record cadence, but the consuming loader and field semantics are still
00099920                            ; unresolved, so keep the names structural.
00099920                            
